pull.title: test: Set catch_system_errors=no on boost unit tests
pull.body:
Closes #16700  

Can be tested by adding an `assert(0)` and then running either `make check` or `./src/test/test_bitcoin -t bla_tests --catch_system_errors=no/yes`
